      "kind": "blog",
      "heading": "Building My First SSG",
      "body": "# Building My First SSG\n\nI decided to build a static site generator to better understand how they work.\n\n## The Architecture\n\nThe basic flow is simple:\n1. Read markdown files\n2. Convert to HTML\n3. Apply templates\n4. Generate static pages\n\n## Challenges\n\n- Template rendering\n- Asset management\n- Performance optimization\n\nIt's been a great learning experience!",
      "section_ref": "root",
