      "kind": "blog",
      "heading": "Coffee and Code",
      "body": "# Coffee and Code\n\nThere's something special about coding in a good cafe.\n\n## My Favorite Spots\n\n- The Corner Cafe: Great wifi, excellent espresso\n- Code & Brew: Developer-friendly atmosphere\n- The Quiet Corner: Perfect for deep work\n\n## Tips for Cafe Coding\n\n1. Bring headphones\n2. Order early to secure a good spot\n3. Be respectful of space during busy hours\n\nHappy coding!",
      "section_ref": "root",
      "draft": false,
