      "kind": "blog",
      "heading": "Working Remotely: One Year In",
      "body": "# Working Remotely: One Year In\n\nIt's been a year since I went fully remote. Here are my thoughts.\n\n## The Good\n\n- No commute\n- Flexible schedule\n- Better work-life balance\n\n## The Challenges\n\n- Isolation can be real\n- Home distractions\n- Harder to separate work and life\n\n## My Setup\n\n- Dedicated workspace\n- Regular video calls with the team\n- Daily walks to break up the day\n\nOverall: 10/10 would recommend!",
      "section_ref": "root",
